valueTransl: U suprotnom smijeru od kazaljke na satu

valueEn: 0: Solid gravel/packed earth, no obstacles, wide curves
valueTransl: 0: Tvrd tucanik/nabijena zemlja, bez prepreka, blage krivine

valueEn: 1: Some loose surface, small obstacles, wide curves
valueTransl: 1: Malo neravna površina, male prepreke, blage krivine

valueEn: 2: Much loose surface, large obstacles, easy hairpins
valueTransl: 2: Više neravna površina, velike prepreke, lakše krivine

valueEn: 3: Slippery surface, large obstacles, tight hairpins
valueTransl: 3: Sklizava površina, velike prepreke, uske krivine

valueEn: 4: Loose surface or boulders, dangerous hairpins
valueTransl: 4: Neravna površina ili veliko kamenje, opasne krivine
5: Maksimalno težak teren, polja kamenih gromada, odroni

valueEn: 6: Not rideable except by the very best mountain bikers
valueTransl: 6: Nije za vožnju osim za najbolje brdske bicikliste

labelTransl: Težina uspona staze za brdski biciklizam
valueEn: 0: Avg. incline <10%, gravel/packed earth, no obstacles
valueTransl: 0: Prosječan nagib <10%, tucanik/nabijena zemlja, bez prepreka

valueEn: 1: Avg. incline <15%, gravel/packed earth, few small objects
valueTransl: 1: Prosječan nagib <15%, tucanik/nabijena zemlja, manje prepreke

valueEn: 2: Avg. incline <20%, stable surface, fistsize rocks/roots
valueTransl: 2: Prosječan nagib <20%, stabilna površina, kamenje veličine šake/korijenje

valueEn: 3: Avg. incline <25%, variable surface, fistsize rocks/branches
valueTransl: 3: Prosječan nagib <25%, raznolika površina, kamenje veličine šake/granje

valueEn: 4: Avg. incline <30%, poor condition, big rocks/branches
valueTransl: 4: Prosječan nagib <30%, loši uvjeti, veliko kamenje/granje

valueEn: 5: Very steep, bike generally needs to be pushed or carried
valueTransl: 5: Jako strmo, bicikl je uglavnom potrebno gurati ili nositi

valueEn: In smoking areas, not physically isolated
Robust Wheels: trekking bike, car, rickshaw
High Clearance: light duty off-road vehicle
Solid: paved or heavily compacted hardcore surface
Mostly Solid: gravel/rock with some soft material mixed in
Even mixture of hard and soft materials
Mostly Soft: soil/sand/grass with some hard material mixed in
Excellent: unambiguous path or markers everywhere
Good: markers visible, sometimes require searching
Intermediate: few markers, path mostly visible
Bad: no markers, path sometimes invisible/pathless
Horrible: often pathless, some orientation skills required
No: pathless, excellent orientation skills required
